t;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><i><span lang=EN-US  style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Dari  Abu Abdurrahman, Abdullah bin Umar bin Alh- Khottob radiallahuanhuma dia  berkata </span></i><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>: Saya mendengar Rasulullah </span><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"AGA Arabesque";  mso-ascii-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'><span  style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'>e</span></span><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'> bersabda : Islam dibangun diatas </span><st1:City><st1:place><span    lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:    "Bookman Old Style"'>lima</span></st1:place></st1:City><span lang=EN-US  style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>  perkara; Bersaksi bahwa tiada Ilah yang berhak disembah selain Allah dan bahwa  nabi Muhammad utusan Allah, menegakkan shalat, menunaikan zakat, melaksanakan  haji dan puasa Ramadhan. <span style='mso-tab-count:1'>         </span><span  style='mso-spacerun:yes'>         </span></span><i><span lang=EN-US  style='mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>(Riwayat  Turmuzi dan Muslim)<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:8.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><u><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Pelajaran  yang terdapat dalam hadis / </span></u></b><b><u><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL  style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1575;&#1604;&#1601;&#1608;&#1575;&#1574;&#1583;  &#1605;&#1606; &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></u></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><u><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Rasulullah  </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;  font-family:"AGA Arabesque";mso-ascii-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:  "AGA Arabesque"'><span style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'>e</span></span><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'> menyamakan Islam dengan bangunan yang kokoh dan tegak  diatas tiang-tiang yang mantap. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Pernyataan  tentang keesaan Allah dan keberadaannya, membenarkan kenabian Muhammad </span><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"AGA Arabesque";  mso-ascii-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'><span  style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'>e</span></span><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>merupakan hal  yang paling mendasar dibanding rukun-rukun yang lainnya.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Selalu  menegakkan shalat dan menunaikannya secara sempurna dengan syarat rukunnya,  adab-adabnya dan sunnah-sunnahnya agar dapat memberikan buahnya dalam diri  seorang muslim yaitu meninggalkan perbuatan keji dan munkar karena shalat  mencegah seseorang dari perbuatan keji dan munkar. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Wajib  mengeluarkan zakat dari harta orang kaya yang syarat-syarat wajibnya zakat  sudah ada pada mereka lalu memberikannya kepada orang-orang fakir dan yang  membutuhkan. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>5.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Wajibnya  menunaikan ibadah haji dan puasa (Ramadhan) bagi setiap muslim. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>6.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Adanya  keterkaitan rukun Islam satu sama lain. Siapa yang mengingkarinya maka dia  bukan seorang muslim berdasarkan ijma’. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>7.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Nash  diatas menunjukkan bahwa rukun Islam ada </span><st1:City><st1:place><span    lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:    "Bookman Old Style"'>lima</span></st1:place></st1:City><span lang=EN-US  style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>,  dan masih banyak lagi perkara lain yang penting dalam Islam yang tidak  ditunjukkan dalam hadis. Rasulullah </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"AGA Arabesque";mso-ascii-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-char-typ