aqidah dan amal perbuatan. Tidak bermanfaat amal tanpa iman demikian  juga tidak bermanfaat iman tanpa amal .<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><u><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Tema-tema  hadis / </span></u></b><b><u><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;  mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1608;&#1590;&#1608;&#1593;&#1575;&#1578;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></u></b><span dir=LTR></span><b><u><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :</span></u></b><b><u><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:4.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><u><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  2.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p><span   style='text-decoration:none'>&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></u></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>1. Wala’  dan Bara’ dalam syahadatain<span style='mso-tab-count:1'> </span>: <b>2</b> :  256, </span><st1:time Minute="36" Hour="16"><b><span lang=EN-US   style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bi