#1615;&#1607;&#1615;&#1605;&#1618;  &#1593;&#1614;&#1604;&#1614;&#1609; &#1575;&#1604;&#1604;&#1607;&#1616;  &#1578;&#1614;&#1593;&#1614;&#1575;&#1604;&#1609;&#1614;<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal align=right dir=RTL style='text-align:left'><span  lang=AR-SA style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Simplified Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";color:black'>[&#1585;&#1608;&#1575;&#1607;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1576;&#1582;&#1575;&#1585;&#1610;  &#1608;&#1605;&#1587;&#1604;&#1605; ]<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal align=right dir=RTL style='text-align:left'><span  lang=AR-SA style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Simplified Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";color:black'>Kosa kata / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA  dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";color:black'>&#1605;&#1601;&#1585;&#1583;&#1575;&#1578;</span></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";color:black'><span dir=LTR></span>  :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal align=right dir=RTL style='text-align:left'><span  lang=EN-US dir=LTR style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Simplified Arabic";  color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0   style='border-collapse:collapse;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;   mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext'>   <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:0'>    <td width=225 valign=top style='width:168.4pt;border:no