pan  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"AGA Arabesque";  mso-ascii-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'><span  style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'><span  style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span></span></span></i><i><span lang=EN-US  style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"AGA Arabesque";  mso-ascii-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'><span  style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'>e</span></span></i><i><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'> dan kesayangannya </span></i><i><span lang=EN-US  style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"AGA Arabesque";  mso-ascii-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'><span  style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'>y</span></span></i><i><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'> dia berkata</span></i><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'> :  Saya menghafal dari Rasulullah </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"AGA Arabesque";mso-ascii-font-family:  "MCS P_Mohammad.";mso-hansi-font-family:"MCS P_Mohammad.";mso-char-type:symbol;  mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'><span style='mso-char-type:symbol;  mso-symbol-font-family:"AGA Arabesque"'>e</span></span><span lang=EN-US  style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>  (sabdanya): Tinggalkanlah apa yang meragukanmu kepada apa yang tidak  meragukanmu.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal align=right style='text-align:right;direction:ltr;  unicode-bidi:embed'><i><span lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>(Riwayat Turmuzi dan dia berkata:  Hadisnya hasan shoheh)</span></i><span lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-size:  18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>Pelajaran:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Meninggalkan  syubhat dan mengambil yang halal akan melahirkan sikap <i>wara’</i>. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Keluar  dari <i>ikhtilaf</i> ulama lebih utama karena hal tersebut lebih terhindar dari  perbuatan syubhat, khususnya jika diantara pendapat mereka tidak ada yang dapat  dikuatkan. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Jika  keraguan bertentangan dengan keyakinan maka keyakinan yang diambil. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Sebuah  perkara harus jelas berdasarkan keyakinan dan ketenangan. Tidak ada harganya  keraguan dan kebimbangan.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>5.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Berhati-hati  dari sikap meremehkan terhadap urusan agama dan masalah bid’ah. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>6.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Siapa yang  membiasakan perkara syubhat maka dia akan berani melakukan perbuatan yang  haram.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Tema  hadis dan ayat yang terkait :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>1.  Meninggalkan keragu-raguan<span style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span>: </span><st1:time  Minute="10" Hour="14"><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:   18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>14</span></b><span   lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:   "Bookman Old Style"'> : 10</span></st1:time><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>, <b>49</b>  : 15, <b>2</b> : 2<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoHeading8 dir=RTL><u><span lang=AR-SA><o:p><span style='text-decoration:   none'>&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></u></p>    <p class=MsoNormal dir=RTL><span lang=EN-US dir=LTR><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    </div>    </body>    
