tyle='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Iman dapat  bertambah dan berkurang, bertambah dengan ketaatan dan berkurang dengan  kemaksiatan. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Anjuran  untuk menyatukan hati. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Tema-tema  hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:18.0pt;  mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1608;&#1590;&#1608;&#1593;&#1575;&#1578;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#158