;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:5.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-tab-count:1'>                        </span></span><i><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>Dari Abu Hurairah radhiallahuanhu sesungguhnya seseorang  bertanya kepada Rasulullah </span></i><i><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"MCS P_Mohammad."'>sholallohu  ‘alaihi wa sallam</span></i><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'> : (Ya  Rasulullah </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  18.0pt;font-family:"MCS P_Mohammad."'><span  style='mso-spacerun:yes'>      </span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>)  nasihatilah saya. Beliau bersabda : Jangan kamu marah. Beliau menanyakan hal  itu berkali-kali. Maka beliau bersabda : Jangan engkau marah. </span><i><span  lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>(Riwayat  Bukhiroi )<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>Pelajaran yang terdapat dalam hadis / </span></b><b><span  lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;  font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1575;&#1604;&#1601;&#1608;&#1575;&#1574;&#1583;  &#1605;&#1606; &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Anjuran  bagi setiap muslim untuk memberikan nasihat dan mengenal perbuatan-perbuatan  kebajikan, menambah wawasan ilmu yang bermanfaat serta memberikan nasihat yang  baik. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Larangan  marah. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Dianjurkan  untuk mengulangi pembicaraan hingga pendengar menyadari pentingnya dan  kedudukannya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Tema  hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;  mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1608;&#1590;&#1608;&#1593;&#1575;&#1578;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span dir=LTR></span><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>1.  Meninggalkan sifat pemarah : <b>3 : </b>159<b>, 3 : </b>134<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal dir=RTL><span lang=EN-US dir=LTR><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    </div>    </b