=AR-SA  dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1578;&#1585;&#1580;&#1605;&#1577;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579; </span></b><span dir=LTR></span><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span><span  style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>:</span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL  style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span><i>Dari Abu Amr, -ada juga yang  mengatakan- : Abu ‘Amrah, Sufyan bin Abdillah Ats Tsaqofi radhiallahuanhu dia  berkata, saya berkata</i> : Wahai Rasulullah </span><i><span lang=EN-US  style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"MCS P_Mohammad."'>shollallohu  ‘alaihi wa sallam</span></i><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>, katakan  kepada saya tentang Islam sebuah perkataan yang<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>tidak<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>saya tanyakan kepada  seorangpun selainmu. Beliau bersabda: Katakanlah: saya beriman kepada Allah,  kemudian berpegang teguhlah .<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>                    </span></span><i><span lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>(Riwayat Muslim). <o:p></o:p></span></i></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Pelajaran  yang terdapat dalam hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL  style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1575;&#1604;&#1601;&#1608;&#1575;&#1574;&#1583;  &#1605;&#1606; &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Iman  kepada Allah ta’ala harus mendahului ketaatan. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Amal saleh  dapat menjaga keimanan<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Iman dan  amal saleh keduanya harus dilaksanakan. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><i><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Istiqomah</span></i><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'> merupakan derajat yang tinggi . <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>5.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Keinginan  yang kuat dari para shahabat dalam menjaga agamanya dan merawat keimanannya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>6.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Perintah  untuk istiqomah dalam tauhid dan ikhlas beribadah hanya kepada Allah semata  hingga mati.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:5.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Tema-tema  hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;  mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1608;&#1590;&#1608;&#1593;&#1575;&#1578;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span dir=LTR></span><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText3 align=left style='margin-left:14.2pt;text-align:left;  text-indent:-14.2pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US>1.  Bertanya untuk mendapatkan kebaikan : <b>2</b> : 149, <b>2</b> : 512, <b>2</b>  : 217, <b>2</b> : 219, <b>2</b> : 219, <b>2</b> :220. </span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Iman dan  istiqomah : <b>41</b> : 30, <b>46 </b>: 13, <b>72</b> : 16, <b>15</b> : 99<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal dir=RTL><span lang=EN-US dir=LTR><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    </div>    </body>    
