/span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal align=right dir=RTL style='text-align:left'><span  lang=AR-SA style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Simplified Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>[&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;  &#1581;&#1587;&#1606; &#1585;&#1608;&#1575;&#1607; &#1575;&#1576;&#1606;  &#1605;&#1575;&#1580;&#1577; &#1608;&#1594;&#1610;&#1585;&#1607;  &#1576;&#1571;&#1587;&#1575;&#1606;&#1610;&#1583; &#1581;&#1587;&#1606;&#1577;]</span><span  lang=AR-SA style='font-size:4.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Simplified Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal align=right dir=RTL style='text-align:left'><span  lang=AR-SA style='font-size:4.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Simplified Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>Kosa kata / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL  style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1601;&#1585;&#1583;&#1575;&#1578;</span></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0   style='border-collapse:collapse;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt'>   <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:0'>    <td width=225 valign=top style='width:168.4pt;border:none;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;    mso-border-right-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt'>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span    lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:9.0pt;    font-family:"Simplified Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1583;&#1604;&#1600;(&#1606;&#1610;)</span><span    dir=LTR></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:9.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:    12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Simplified Arabic"'><span    dir=LTR></span> : Tunjukkan<o:p></o:p></span></p>    </td>    <td width=225 valign=top style='width:168.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt'>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span    lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:9.0pt;    font-family:"Simplified Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1571;&#1581;&#1576;&#1600;(&#1606;&#1610;)</span><span    dir=LTR></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:9.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:    12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Simplified Arabic"'><span    dir=LTR></span> : Mencintai(-ku)<o:p></o:p></span></p>    </td>   </tr>   <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:1;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes'>    <td width=225 style='width:168.4pt;border:none;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;    mso-border-right-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt'>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span    lang=EN-US style='font-size:9.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:    "Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Simplified Arabic"'><span    style='mso-spacerun:yes'>             </span>(kepadaku)</span><span    lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:9.0pt;    font-family:"Simplified Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>    </td>    <td width=225 valign=top style='width:168.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt'>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span    lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:9.0pt;    font-family:"Simplified Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1575;&#1586;&#1607;&#1583;</span><span    dir=LTR></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:9.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:    12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Simplified Arabic"'><span    dir=LTR></span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>: Bersikap <i>zuhud</i>-lah<o:p></o:p></span></p>    </td>   </tr>  </table>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span  lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:5.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:  "Simplified Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>Terjemah hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL  style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1578;&#1585;&#1580;&#1605;&#1577;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span>Dari Abu Abbas Sahl bin Sa’ad Assa’idi<i>  radhiallahuanhu </i>dia berkata : Seseorang mendatangi Rasulullah </span><i><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"MCS P_Mohammad."'>shollallohu  ‘alaihi wa sallam</span></i><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>, maka  beliau berkata : Wahai Rasulullah, tunjukkan kepadaku sebuah amalan yang jika  aku kerjakan, Allah dan manusia akan mencintaiku, maka beliau bersabda:  Zuhudlah terhadap dunia maka engkau akan dicintai Allah dan zuhudlah terhadap  apa yang ada pada manusia maka engkau akan dicintai manusia.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><i><span  lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>(Hadis  hasan riwayat Ibnu Majah dan lainnya dengan sanad hasan) .<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>    <p class=MsoNormal align=right style='text-align:right;direction:ltr;  unicode-bidi:embed'><i><span lang=EN-US style='mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Pelajaran  yang terdapat dalam hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL  style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1575;&#1604;&#1601;&#1608;&#1575;&#1574;&#1583;  &#1605;&#1606; &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span>:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Menuntut  kecukupan terhadap dunia adalah perkara wajib, sedang zuhud adalah tidak adanya  keter-gantungan dan terpusatnya perhatian<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>terhadapnya . <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Bersikap  qanaah terhadap rezeki yang halal dan ridho terhadapnya serta bersikap ‘iffah  dari perbuatan haram dan hati-hati terhadap syubhat. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Jiwa yang  merasa cukup dan iffah serta berkorban dengan harta dan jiwa di jalan Allah  merupakan hakekat zuhud. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Tema-tema  hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;  mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1608;&#1590;&#1608;&#1593;&#1575;&#1578;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span dir=LTR></span><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Zuhud<span  style='mso-tab-count:1'>     </span>: </span><st1:time Minute="45" Hour="18"><b><span   lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:   "Bookman Old Style"'>18</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;   mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'> : 45</span></st1:time><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>-46, <b>29</b> : 64, <b>102</b> : 1-5<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Menghindari  penyakit hasad (dengki) : <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal dir=RTL><span lang=EN-US dir=LTR><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    </div>    </body>    
