"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Pelajaran  yang terdapat dalam hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL  style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1575;&#1604;&#1601;&#1608;&#1575;&#1574;&#1583;  &#1605;&#1606; &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text-kashida:0%;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:  list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Menentang  pelaku kebatilan dan menolak kemunkaran adalah kewajiban yang dituntut dalam  ajaran Islam atas setiap muslim sesuai kemampuan dan kekuatannya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:  kashida;text