>       </span></span><span  lang=AR-SA style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>[&#1585;&#1608;&#1575;&#1607;  &#1605;&#1587;&#1604;&#1605;]</span><span lang=AR-SA style='font-size:18.0pt;  mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'> <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:  0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Kosa kata  / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:  11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1601;&#1585;&#1583;&#1575;&#1578;</span></b><span  dir=LTR></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0   style='border-collapse:collapse;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt'>   <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:0'>    <td width=225 valign=top style='width:168.4pt;border:none;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;    mso-border-right-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt'>    <p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:kashida;text-kashida:    0%;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span dir=RTL></span><span lang=AR-SA    dir=RTL style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";    mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=RTL></span><