>  </table>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=right style='text-align:right;direction:ltr;  unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=left style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;  unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Terjemah hadis / </span></b><b><span  lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;  font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>&#1578;&#1585;&#1580;&#1605;&#1577;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579;</span></b><span dir=LTR></span><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span> :</span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA  dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='text-align:justify;text-indent:14.2pt;direction:  ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Dari Ibnu Umar <i>radhiallahuanhuma</i>  berkata : Rasulullah saw memegang pundak kedua pundak saya seraya bersabda :  Jadilah engkau di dunia seakan-akan orang asing atau pengembara “, Ibnu Umar  berkata : Jika kamu berada di sore hari jangan tunggu pagi hari, dan jika kamu  berada di pagi hari jangan tunggu sore hari, gunakanlah kesehatanmu untuk  (persiapan saat) sakitmu dan kehidupanmu untuk kematianmu “ (Riwayat Bukhori) <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=left style='text-align:left;direction:ltr;  unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:14.2pt;  direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Pelajaran  :<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Bersegera  mengerjakan pekerjaan baik dan memperbanyak ketaatan, tidak lalai dan  menunda-nunda<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>karena dia tidak tahu  kapan datang ajalnya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Menggunakan  berbagai kesempatan dan momentum sebelum hilangnya berlalu .<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Zuhud di  dunia berarti tidak bergantung kepadanya hingga mengabaikan ibadah kepada Allah  ta’ala untuk kehidupan akhirat. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Hati-hati  dan khawatir dari azab Allah adalah sikap seorang musafir yang  bersungguh-sungguh dan hati –hati agar tidak tersesat. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>5.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Waspada  dari teman yang buruk hingga tidak terhalang dari tujuannya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>6.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Pekerjaan  dunia dituntut untuk menjaga jiwa dan mendatangkan manfaat, seorang muslim  hendaknya menggunakan semua itu untuk tujuan akhirat.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>7.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Bersungguh-sungguh  menjaga waktu dan mempersiapkan diri untuk kematian dan bersegera bertaubat dan  beramal shaleh. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:  -18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:  embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>8.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Rasulullah  memegang kedua pundak Abdullah bin Umar, adalah agar beliau memperhatikan apa  yang akan beliau sampaikan. Menunjukkan bahwa seorang pelajar harus diajarkan  tentang perhatian gurunya kepadanya dan kesungguhannya untuk menyampaikan ilmu  kedalam jiwanya. Hal ini dapat menyebabkan masuknya ilmu, sebagaimana hal itu  juga menunjukkan kecintaan Rasulullah kepada Abdullah bin Umar, karena hal  tersebut pada umumnya dilakukan oleh seseorang kepada siapa yang dicintainya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=right style='text-align:right;direction:ltr;  unicode-bidi:embed'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:  18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:18.0pt;  direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Tema-tema  hadis / </span></b><b><span lang=AR-SA dir=RTL style='font-size:16.0pt;  mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Traditional Arabic";mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'>&#1605;&#1608;&#1590;&#1608;&#1593;&#1575;&#1578;  &#1575;&#1604;&#1581;&#1583;&#1610;&#1579; </span></b><span dir=LTR></span><b><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><span dir=LTR></span><span  style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=left style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:left;  text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:  ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Hakikat  kehidupan : <b>3</b> : 185, </span><st1:time Minute="24" Hour="10"><b><span   lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:   "Bookman Old Style"'>10</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;   mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'> : 24</span></st1:time><span  lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:  "Bookman Old Style"'><o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoBodyText align=left style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:left;  text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 18.0pt;direction:  ltr;unicode-bidi:embed'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:  11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";  mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style";mso-bidi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'><span  style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;  mso-bidi-font-size:18.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:"Bookman Old Style"'>Optimalisasi  setiap kesempatan : <b>103</b> : 1-3, <b>94</b> : 7.<o:p></o:p></span></p>    <p class=MsoNormal dir=RTL><span lang=EN-US dir=LTR><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>    </div>    </body>    
